  <title>Machine Grouting Method</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">Machine Grouting Method</para>
    </header>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px; font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Mark the machine positioning location on the floor considering machine front edge/splash guard reference dimensions as shown in <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="1_6-Preparation-of-Foundation" anchor="Fig1.13" style="color:#0000ff;">Chapter 2 Figure 1.13</link>.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Mark the position of holes &quot;a&quot; with reference to the machine location as shown in <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="1_6-Preparation-of-Foundation" anchor="Fig1.13" style="color:#0000ff;">Chapter 2 Figure 1.13</link>.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:8px;">Install the anchor as shown in installation procedure. (Refer to <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="Fig1.1" style="color:#0000ff;">Figure 1.1</link>)</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:6px;"><text style="font-weight:bold;">Anchor Details</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="margin-top:6px; margin-bottom:6px;">Refer to <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="false" type="topiclink" href="" anchor="Fig1.1" style="color:#0000ff;">Figure 1.1</link> for anchor locations.</para>
